Package com.example.footlongsubs

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddSubActivity
    The AddSubActivity class collects user inputs for adding a new activity and passes them back to the main activity.
    AllSubscriptions
    The AllSubscriptions class contains an ArrayList of Subscriptions as well as a number of methods to manage the list, including addition, deletion, and summing totals.
    BuildConfig  
    CustomAdapter
    Custom Adapter provides the adapter to add the Subscriptions in the AllSubscriptions object to the ListView display Based on https://guides.codepath.com/android/Using-a-BaseAdapter-with-ListView Retrieved 2018-02-05
    EditSubActivity
    The EditSubActivity class collects gives the user the ability to edit a subscription's information or delete it outright from the SubBook
    MainActivity
    The MainActivity is the most important part of the app and bridges the UI and data elements It is reponsible for maintaining persistence, responding to button presses, and displaying the list and sum total.
